reviewText: my Teknoman English DUB DVD is complete and I can't wait to get the original version!

I have always wanted to see how this show ended.

In American TV we never got past about halfway through this series.
Four stars cause the ending was a little lackluster but I liked the series as a whole.

Arrived before estimated time, brand new, well packed. Ah this Anime classic brings back fond memory's of being a young lad. Watching this on Cheese tv on Channel Ten network in Australia, and still a fan after all these years of anime martial arts & sci fi combo.
